    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "that \"new perspective\" stuff just sounds like more work. more trying. more fighting against something that's clearly inevitable. it's not a story i'm writing, it's a cage. and the only way to actually stop the cycle, to finally get some peace from the constant noise of failing, is to just step out of it entirely. i don't mean a fresh start, i mean a permanent end to the loop.",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
